fields.description:
Description:
1.Run the code snippet below:
{code}
var win1 = Titanium.UI.createWindow({  
    backgroundColor:'#000'
});
   
var usernameField = Ti.UI.createTextField({
		width:'auto',
		height:'auto',
		hintText: 'Username',
		top: 10, 
		left: 10
});
win1.add(usernameField);
win1.open()
{code}

Actual result:
1.You will see that the textfield is not displayed
2.Setting the width & height to specific dimensions displays the textfield

Expected Result:
The text field should be displayed
